---
import Icon from '../ui/Icon.astro';
---

#yeah currently under development, but this is the general idea of how we want to present the trials. We want to have a clear pro and con side, with a quote and some key points for each. The design is meant to be clean and modern, with a focus on readability and visual hierarchy.
#I am not sure if i would implement this tho 
#This may be just distraction from the main content 

#To Do : Implement a way to collect user feedback on the trials, maybe a simple voting system or comment section. This would allow us to gauge public opinion and potentially adjust the content based on user input.

<section id="trials" class="py-24 px-8 md:px-12 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase text-primary tracking-widest border border-primary px-4 py-1">Currently under Development</span>
      <h2 class="font-headline text-5xl mt-6">Should we prioritize the collective or the individual?</h2>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 border-2 border-secondary divide-y-2 md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x-2 divide-secondary">
      <div class="p-12 bg-surface-container-low">
        <h3 class="font-label text-xl font-bold mb-8 text-secondary">The Collective (Pro)</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-xl leading-relaxed italic mb-8">
          "No man is an island. Our flourishing is inextricably linked to the health of the community. We sacrifice the ego to ensure the survival and prosperity of the whole."
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 font-label text-xs">
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="check" class="mr-2 h-3 w-3" /> Shared Resource Security</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="check" class="mr-2 h-3 w-3" /> Systematic Resilience</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="check" class="mr-2 h-3 w-3" /> Inherited Wisdom Loops</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <div class="p-12 bg-white">
        <h3 class="font-label text-xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary">The Individual (Con)</h3>
        <p class="font-body text-xl leading-relaxed italic mb-8">
          "The smallest minority on earth is the individual. Those who deny individual rights cannot claim to be defenders of minorities. The collective is an abstraction; only the person is real."
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 font-label text-xs">
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="bolt" class="mr-2 h-3 w-3" /> Sovereign Agency</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="bolt" class="mr-2 h-3 w-3" /> Creative Non-conformity</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="bolt" class="mr-2 h-3 w-3" /> Moral Responsibility</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
